<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٣٩١ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ , عَنِ الْحَسَنِ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَنْ كَذَّبَ بِالْقَدَرِ فَقَدْ كَذَّبَ بِالْقُرْآنِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>